text: Hot Chelle Rae is an American pop rock band. They formed near Nashville, Tennessee around 2005. Their debut album Lovesick Electric was released in 2009. The band is best known for their 2011 song, "Tonight Tonight". ==References== category:American pop music groups Category:American rock bands Category:Emo bands Category:Musical groups from Tennessee Category:2005 establishments in the United States Category:2000s establishments in Tennessee Category:Musical groups established in 2005
